Defendant Sean A Ellis in court.  Attorney Ann M. Larson in court for Sean A Ellis.  Prosecuting attorney Angelina R Scarpelli in court for the State of Wisconsin. 
NO CONTEST to the charge in count 1, felony bail jumping.   Convicted.
Sentence withheld and defendant is placed on probation to DOC for two (2) years.
Conditions of probation:
1) Assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Departments assessment process;
2) Have no contact with anyone under the age of 18 unless otherwise approved by the agent.
3) Provide DNA sample
4) Maintain fulltime employment, schooling, work search or combination;
5) Pay court costs;
6) Pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC.
